{"GYL56abLbw5":{"id":"GYL56abLbw5","type":"work","title":"浣水續談","authors":[{"name":"朱孟震","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《浣水續談》•一卷","author_info":"明朱孟震撰","summary":"明朱孟震撰。是編乃萬曆十三年孟震官四川按察使時所作，故以浣水為名。浣水者，浣花溪也。其書雜撮而成，往往不著時代，亦不著出典。如并州士族好為可笑詩賦一條，蓋《顏氏家訓》之原文，而孟震筆之於己書，儼如新事。然則所謂誂撆邢、魏諸公者，不幾為明代之邢、魏乎？惟松柏灘觀音寺一條，考詢遺老，繪畫地圖，核其墳塔名氏，師弟世系，知所謂雪菴和尚者在有無疑似之間，特為明確。","edition":"浙江吳玉墀家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=450819","type":"text","details":"（明朱孟震撰"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlikezhubingqiquan","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02056615","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆刻朱秉器全集本","version":"v2","total_page":119,"paragraph_count":1108,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56aA68Hm":{"id":"GYL56aA68Hm","type":"work","title":"對問編","authors":[{"name":"江應曉","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《對問編》•八卷","author_info":"明江應曉撰","summary":"明江應曉撰。應曉字覺卿，徽州人。嘉靖末官涪州州判。是書刺取史籍所載天文、地理、人物、雜事分條立說，議論多偏駁不純。前有自序一篇，文頗聱牙。蓋亦沿曆下、琅琊之習者也。","edition":"副都御史黃登賢家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":8},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=4683093","type":"text","details":"（明江應曉撰"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02056585","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆刻本","version":"v1","total_page":300,"paragraph_count":2570,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56aeuWab":{"id":"GYL56aeuWab","type":"work","title":"游宦餘談","authors":[{"name":"朱孟震","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《游宦餘談》•一卷","author_info":"明朱孟震撰","summary":"明朱孟震撰。自序稱生平宦轍，殆遍九州，因摭耳目所及，撰成此書。初分五卷，後乃並為一卷。所錄多瑣事。末附西南夷風土記二十六條，頗為詳明。然孟震序中自言，未至滇雲，則惟據傳聞書之，恐亦未盡確實矣。","edition":"江西巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=8012325","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlikezhubingqiquan","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02056616","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆刻朱秉器全集本","version":"v2","total_page":143,"paragraph_count":1389,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56aHYkYw":{"id":"GYL56aHYkYw","type":"work","title":"應菴任意錄","authors":[{"name":"羅鶴","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《應菴任意錄》•十四卷","author_info":"明羅鶴撰","summary":"明羅鶴撰。鶴字子應，號應菴，泰和人。是書計二百四十四條。大意欲仿《容齋隨筆》、《學齋佔畢》諸書，而耳目頗隘，不能盡有援據考證，多據所聞見，以意褒貶而已。其持論有最偏駁者，如赤龍合慶都生堯，修己坼背生禹，本緯書妄說，皆反覆論辨，以為必然。又引章氏《家譜》、宏益《記聞》、東林《論易語》、尹氏之《性學指要》、趙說之《心學淵源後跋》、胡氏《大同論》一切瑣說，文致周、程諸儒皆以僧為師。至以鄉曲之私，謂建文遜國之時楊士奇不當死難，使務此小節則不足以為東裏，尤為害義。其謂呂後名雉，高祖字之曰野雞之類，杜撰故實，又其小疵矣。","edition":"浙江範懋柱家天一閣藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":14}},"GYL56aQYWHd":{"id":"GYL56aQYWHd","type":"work","title":"聞雁齋筆談","authors":[{"name":"張大複","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《聞雁齋筆談》•六卷","author_info":"明張大複撰","summary":"明張大複撰。是編大抵欲仿蘇軾《志林》，故多似古人雜帖短跋之格。然所推重者李贄，所規摹者屠隆也。","edition":"浙江鮑士恭家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":6},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=872029","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=1569594","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-2","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=4140558","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlisanshisangumeng","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02095812","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆三十三年顧孟兆等刻本","version":"v2","total_page":326,"paragraph_count":2125,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02038389","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v1","total_page":320,"paragraph_count":2538,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56atfanj":{"id":"GYL56atfanj","type":"work","title":"留青日劄","authors":[{"name":"田藝衡","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《留青日劄》•三十九卷","author_info":"明田藝衡撰","summary":"明田藝衡撰。藝衡有《大明同文集》，已著錄。是書欲仿《容齋隨筆》、《夢溪筆談》，而所學不足以逮之，故蕪雜特甚。其中詩談初編、二編各一卷，玉笑零音一卷，大統曆解三卷，始天易一卷，皆以所著別行之書編入，以足卷帙，尤可不必。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":39},"resources":[{"id":"shidianguji-mingwanliyuankeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NGJ892411999028140148252","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"明萬曆元年刻本","version":"v3","total_page":1265,"paragraph_count":3542,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-mingwanliyuankeben-1","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NGJ892411999032690163883","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"明萬曆元年刻本","version":"v1","total_page":1266,"paragraph_count":3493,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56aiX75Z":{"id":"GYL56aiX75Z","type":"work","title":"黃帝祠額解","authors":[{"name":"李維楨","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《黃帝祠額解》•一卷","author_info":"明李維楨撰","summary":"明李維楨撰。維楨有《史通評釋》，已著錄。是書乃其奉詔謁黃帝陵，見舊祠取鼎湖之事，額曰龍髯。乃作是書以辨其不經，謂騎龍即乘六龍之義。其實《子華子》已有是說，無庸複贅。又舉百家所言黃帝神靈諸事，一一駁詰，詞極辨博。實亦司馬遷五帝本紀文不雅馴，薦紳難言之緒論也。","edition":"兩江總督采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"shidianguji-wanlishenshishangbai","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY6410","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆沈氏尚白齋刻本","version":"v2","total_page":32,"paragraph_count":20,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56a2rwHq":{"id":"GYL56a2rwHq","type":"work","title":"青林雜錄","authors":[{"name":"王薰","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《青林雜錄》•一卷","author_info":"明王薰撰","summary":"明王薰撰。薰字簡之，天臺人。嘉靖中為黃岩縣學生。是書蓋其隨筆記錄之文，後人抄而傳之者。如第五頁中一條，上書一脀字，下注實物於器之名六字，別無他語，可以知其非著書也。中多講學之語，亦多憤激之談。如謂越有貴人操予奪之權，寵辱進退，惟其所專制。有三人謁之，一翼之行，舉為邑；一為供僕隸之役，舉為郡；一為奉溺器，遂舉為郡邑長。小賤則小貴，大賤則大貴云云。雖寓言以鳴不平，亦失之太甚矣。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1}},"GYL56aDhinj":{"id":"GYL56aDhinj","type":"work","title":"孤竹賓談","authors":[{"name":"陳德文","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《孤竹賓談》•四卷","author_info":"明陳德文撰","summary":"明陳德文撰。德文號石陽山人，吉水人。嘉靖中以順天府尹行部永平，館於夷齊廟。公事餘間，隨筆紀載。以永平為古孤竹國，故以《孤竹賓談》名書。其中論斷，率多僻謬。如謂唐之房、杜不過一文人墨士。滕文公恨不與孔子生同時，扶蘇、蒙恬得矯詔，當舉兵稱王之類。皆謬悠之談，不足辨也。","edition":"兩淮鹽政采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":4},"resources":[{"id":"shidianguji-sujibaiyidaomingjiaj","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NGJ892411999027180156848","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"蘇繼白以道明嘉靖28年刻本","version":"v2","total_page":170,"paragraph_count":1302,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56aqkJ5V":{"id":"GYL56aqkJ5V","type":"work","title":"說頤","authors":[{"name":"餘懋學","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《說頤》•八卷","author_info":"明餘懋學撰","summary":"明餘懋學撰。懋學字行之，婺源人。隆慶戊辰進士，官至南京戶部右侍郎。天啟中追諡恭穆。事蹟具《明史•本傳》。是書凡三百五十二則，每則徵引古事相類或相反者二條，撮為四字標題，而以論斷數語綴其末。旁見側出，頗得連珠遺意。然引事不標出典，置論亦多庸膚。","edition":"兩淮鹽政采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":8},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=2752143","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlisanshiliuzhifan","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02056617","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆三十六年直方堂刻本","version":"v2","total_page":580,"paragraph_count":5141,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56a6XDeF":{"id":"GYL56a6XDeF","type":"work","title":"厭次瑣談","authors":[{"name":"劉世偉","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《厭次瑣談》•一卷","author_info":"明劉世偉撰","summary":"明劉世偉撰。世偉字宗周，陽信人。嘉靖中官寧州州同。其書雜取古人說部而評論之，所見頗淺。又載宋江誘柴進為盜事，尤俚俗附會之說。末附談後二十八條。其曰厭次者，以陽信乃漢厭次縣地也。","edition":"浙江範懋柱家天一閣藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=3062295","type":"text","details":"（明劉世偉撰"},{"id":"shidianguji-chaoben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02056584","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"鈔本","version":"v4","total_page":69,"paragraph_count":85,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56aLvunf":{"id":"GYL56aLvunf","type":"work","title":"梅花草堂筆談","authors":[{"name":"張大複","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《梅花草堂筆談》•十四卷、《二談》•六卷","author_info":"明張大複撰","summary":"明張大複撰。大複字元長，昆山人。是編為其《梅花草堂集》中之一種，據《江南通志•文苑傳》，乃其喪明以後追憶而作也。所記皆同社酬答之語，間及鄉里瑣事，辭意纖佻，無關考證。第十三卷中有論孟解十二條，以釋家語詮解聖經，殊屬支離。二談輕佻尤甚。如雲《水滸傳》何所不有，卻無破老一事（案：美男破老，《逸周書》之文），非關闕陷，恰是酒肉漢本色如此，以此益知作者之妙。是何言歟？","edition":"兩江總督采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":14},"additional_works":[{"book_title":"二談","n_juan":6}],"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/梅花草堂筆談","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=485315","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=4373037","type":"text","details":"張大複著"}]},"GYL56axBoao":{"id":"GYL56axBoao","type":"work","title":"玉笑零音","authors":[{"name":"田藝衡","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《玉笑零音》•一卷","author_info":"明田藝衡撰","summary":"明田藝衡撰。是書皆採取新奇故事，緯以儷語，凡一百二十八條。其中如以堯、舜之讓天下為愛身，不與朱、均以天下為愛子。舜、禹之受天下為不知害，鑄鼎為鎮厭之術，金縢為詛咒之媒，皆紕繆之甚者。已編入所著《留青日劄》中，此乃其初出別行之本也。","edition":"兩江總督采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/玉笑零音","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=854349","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY5902","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v3","total_page":34,"paragraph_count":26,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56an61j5":{"id":"GYL56an61j5","type":"work","title":"木幾冗談","authors":[{"name":"彭汝讓","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《木幾冗談》•一卷","author_info":"明彭汝讓撰","summary":"明彭汝讓撰。汝讓字欽之，青浦人。是編乃劄記清言，儇佻殊甚，蓋屠隆一派也。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/木幾冗談","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=84710","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlishenshishangbai","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY6335","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆沈氏尚白齋刻本","version":"v3","total_page":26,"paragraph_count":21,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56aUFUVV":{"id":"GYL56aUFUVV","type":"work","title":"河上楮談","authors":[{"name":"朱孟震","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《河上楮談》•三卷","author_info":"明朱孟震撰","summary":"明朱孟震撰。孟震字秉器，新淦人。隆慶戊辰進士，官至右副都御史，巡撫山西。是書多述舊聞軼事，間或評論詩文，考證典籍，亦頗喜談神怪。其停雲小志一卷，記當時文士頗詳，所載詩篇，多可採錄。其論文宗王世貞，推為明代第一，則當時耳目所染，無足深怪。其辨王禕、吳雲事甚有典據，而遜國一事全沿史彬《致身錄》之訛，引證愈多，舛謬愈甚，與所論元順帝出宋後事，同一誤信之失。其論《史記》訛字最確，而前輩博雅一條，不知《清江集》之現存。又誤以《孔傳六帖》為三孔所作，疏駁亦甚矣。","edition":"江西巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":3},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=535988","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=7172457","type":"text","details":"（明朱孟震撰"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02056611","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v7","total_page":756,"paragraph_count":1719,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlikanben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NA06579","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆07年刊本","version":"v3","total_page":378,"paragraph_count":3594,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56aXmhHZ":{"id":"GYL56aXmhHZ","type":"work","title":"汾上續談","authors":[{"name":"朱孟震","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《汾上續談》•一卷","author_info":"明朱孟震撰","summary":"明朱孟震撰。其體例與《河上楮談》同，而所記多瑣事，惟安南國試錄一條，敍述頗詳，足資考證。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=617332","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=3584160","type":"text","details":"（明朱孟震撰"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02095724","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆刻本","version":"v2","total_page":108,"paragraph_count":1008,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true}}